      • setRestAdapterBuilder

        public ServiceSupportConfiguration setRestAdapterBuilder(RestAdapter.Builder restAdapterBuilder)
        Optionally set a custom RestAdapter.Builder. Note that the SDK will effectively override any values set by RestAdapter.Builder#setClient(Client) or RestAdapter.Builder#setEndpoint(String) by calling RestAdapter.Builder#setClient(Client) with the value returned from getOkHttpClient() and also calling RestAdapter.Builder#setEndpoint(String) and supplying the endpoint value provided in the AndroidManifest.xml com.palomamobile.android.sdk.Endpoint metadata element.
        Parameters:
